OL,3,CFamily 'lost everything' in seconds
OL,4,Cafter e-bike fire destroyed home
OL,6,FA father whose home was destroyed in a
OL,7,Ffire started by a charging e-bike
OL,8,Fbattery said he lost everything in
OL,9,F"seconds".
OL,11,FSimon Blanshard is warning of the
OL,12,F"devastating consequences" of lithium-
OL,13,Fion batteries after a fire ripped
OL,14,Fthrough the property in Bentley,
OL,15,FDoncaster.
OL,17,FInvestigators found the fire started
OL,18,Fafter a battery was left on to charge.
