OL,6,FMr Blanshard said: "It took ten to 15
OL,7,Fseconds for the kitchen to be up in
OL,8,Fflames.
OL,10,F"We have lost everything. We will get
OL,11,Fback on our feet - our memories we
OL,12,Fwill never get back."
OL,14,FMr Blanshard said precious possessions
OL,15,Fhave been destroyed, including his
OL,16,Fdaughter's first certificate from
OL,17,Fschool, which had been displayed on
OL,18,Fthe wall just days before the fire.
