OL,6,F"All my dad's memories were all on top
OL,7,Fof these cupboards and now they are
OL,8,Fall gone," he said.
OL,10,F"I've got no pictures of my kids
OL,11,Fgrowing up. Literally everything lost."
OL,13,FMr Blanshard's son Cameron, 15, was
OL,14,Fthe only person at home when the fire
OL,15,Fstarted earlier this month, but he
OL,16,Fmanaged to escape unharmed and raise
OL,17,Fthe alarm.
OL,19,FMr Blanshard said: "He was asleep on
OL,20,Fthe sofa. He had to get out of the
OL,21,Fdoor somehow.
