OL,6,F"I don't know how he's done it but he
OL,7,Fwas so brave, bless him. (I'm) very
OL,8,Fproud of him for that one."
OL,10,FSouth Yorkshire Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService said 15 fires involving
OL,12,Flithium-ion batteries were recorded in
OL,13,F2023, double the number of the
OL,14,Fprevious year.
OL,16,FBrigade spokesperson Ade Parkin said:
OL,17,F"The people involved in these
OL,18,Fincidents are lucky to have escaped
OL,19,Fwithout serious injury.
