OL,6,F"We know that e-bikes and e-scooters
OL,7,Fare growing in popularity and can be
OL,8,Freally beneficial in opening up
OL,9,Fcycling to people of all fitness
OL,10,Flevels, not to mention the obvious
OL,11,Fenvironmental benefits they bring in
OL,12,Fterms of reduced carbon emissions
OL,13,Fcompared to other means of transport.
OL,15,F"That is why it is so important to
OL,16,Fonly buy bikes from reputable
OL,17,Fsuppliers that show they clearly meet
OL,18,FUK/EU safety laws and only use the
OL,19,Fcharger supplied with the battery."
