OL,6,FMr Parkin said owners should think
OL,7,Fabout where batteries are charged and
OL,8,Fto ensure escape routes are not
OL,9,Fblocked.
OL,11,FNew measures seeking to address e-bike
OL,12,Fand lithium-ion battery fires were
OL,13,Frecently announced in The King's
OL,14,FSpeech.
OL,16,FGiuseppe Capanna, from Electrical
OL,17,FSafety First, said: "When one of these
OL,18,Fbatteries goes into what's called
OL,19,Fthermal runaway, the fire within
OL,20,Fseconds it can just devastate the
OL,21,Fbuilding.
